| 1 | Add global error handler + sanitize error responses | High | Low |
| 2 | Add `helmet` + disable `x-powered-by` | High | Low |
| 3 | Add schema validation (zod / joi / express-validator) before adding input routes | High | Low |
| 4 | Gate `/users` behind auth, drop email from public payload | High | Medium |
| 5 | Add rate limiting | Medium | Low |
| 6 | Body size limits on `express.json()` | Medium | Trivial |
| 7 | `server.on('error')`, signal handlers, process handlers | Medium | Low |
| 8 | Replace `console.*` with structured logger | Low | Medium |

