| Fingerprinting | `app.disable('x-powered-by')` |
| DoS via bodies | `express.json({ limit: '10kb' })` |
| Abuse / brute force | `express-rate-limit` |
| Unvalidated params | `express-validator` with explicit type/range checks + sanitization (`toInt()`) |
| PII disclosure | Removed `email` from unauthenticated `/users` |
| Unknown routes | Explicit 404 handler |
| Crash resilience | `unhandledRejection` / `uncaughtException` + graceful SIGTERM shutdown |
| Testability | `require.main === module` guard so tests can import without binding to port |

