| # | Item | Severity |
|---|---|---|
| 1 | Centralized error middleware + process handlers | **High** |
| 3 | `helmet`, CORS allowlist, rate limit, body size limit | **High** |
| 2 | Schema validation for all inputs | **High** (once inputs exist) |
| 4 | Auth + field filtering on `/users` | **High** |
| 5 | Env-driven port + graceful shutdown | Medium |
| 6 | `asyncHandler` wrapper | Medium |
| 7 | Structured logger | Medium |

