|---|--------|--------|
| 1 | Add centralized error middleware | High — prevents stack-trace leaks |
| 2 | Add `helmet()` + disable `x-powered-by` | High — baseline headers |
| 3 | Bound request body (`express.json({ limit })`) | High — DoS |
