| Global error middleware | Missing | High |
| 404 handler | Missing | Medium |
| Input validation library | Missing | High (once inputs exist) |
| Body size limits | Missing | High |
| `helmet` security headers | Missing | High |
| Rate limiting | Missing | High |
| CORS policy | Missing | Medium |
| Auth on `/users` (PII) | Missing | High |
| `process.on('uncaughtException'...)` | Missing | Medium |
| Graceful shutdown | Missing | Medium |
| Env-based config | Missing | Medium |
| Structured logging with redaction | Missing | Medium |

